fields.title: Spaghetti Carbonara
fields.description: A classic Italian pasta dish made with eggs, cheese, pancetta, and pepper.
fields.ingredients: Spaghetti, Eggs, Parmesan cheese, Pancetta, Black pepper
fields.instructions: 1. Cook spaghetti. 2. Fry pancetta. 3. Mix eggs and cheese. 4. Combine all and serve.

fields.title: Chicken Curry
fields.description: A spicy and flavorful chicken curry with a blend of aromatic spices.
fields.ingredients: Chicken, Curry powder, Coconut milk, Onion, Garlic
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté onions and garlic. 2. Add chicken and curry powder. 3. Stir in coconut milk. 4. Simmer and serve.

fields.title: Margherita Pizza
fields.description: A simple and classic Italian pizza with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella, and basil.
fields.ingredients: Pizza dough, Tomato sauce, Mozzarella, Fresh basil, Olive oil
fields.instructions: 1. Spread sauce on dough. 2. Add mozzarella. 3. Bake and top with fresh basil.

fields.title: Beef Stroganoff
fields.description: A creamy beef dish with mushrooms, sour cream, and onions.
fields.ingredients: Beef strips, Mushrooms, Onions, Sour cream, Beef broth
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté beef and onions. 2. Add mushrooms. 3. Stir in broth and sour cream. 4. Serve over noodles.

fields.title: Vegetable Stir-fry
fields.description: A quick and healthy stir-fry with mixed vegetables and soy sauce.
fields.ingredients: Broccoli, Carrots, Bell peppers, Soy sauce, Garlic, Ginger
fields.instructions: 1. Stir-fry vegetables. 2. Add soy sauce and garlic. 3. Serve with rice.

fields.title: Tacos al Pastor
fields.description: Mexican-style tacos with marinated pork, pineapple, and cilantro.
fields.ingredients: Pork shoulder, Pineapple, Tortillas, Cilantro, Lime
fields.instructions: 1. Marinate and grill pork. 2. Assemble tacos with pineapple and cilantro. 3. Serve with lime.

fields.title: Caesar Salad
fields.description: A classic Caesar salad with crisp lettuce, Parmesan, and Caesar dressing.
fields.ingredients: Romaine lettuce, Parmesan, Croutons, Caesar dressing
fields.instructions: 1. Toss lettuce with dressing. 2. Add Parmesan and croutons.

fields.title: Lemon Garlic Salmon
fields.description: A healthy and flavorful salmon dish with lemon and garlic butter.
fields.ingredients: Salmon fillets, Lemon, Garlic, Butter, Parsley
fields.instructions: 1. Bake salmon with garlic butter. 2. Drizzle with lemon juice and parsley.

fields.title: Chocolate Brownies
fields.description: Rich and fudgy chocolate brownies with a crispy top.
fields.instructions: 1. Melt chocolate and butter. 2. Mix in sugar, eggs, and flour. 3. Bake and enjoy.

fields.title: Thai Green Curry
fields.description: A fragrant and spicy Thai green curry with coconut milk and chicken.
fields.ingredients: Chicken, Green curry paste, Coconut milk, Basil, Bell peppers
fields.instructions: 1. Fry curry paste. 2. Add chicken and coconut milk. 3. Simmer with basil and peppers.

fields.title: Pancakes
fields.description: Fluffy and light pancakes served with maple syrup.
fields.ingredients: Flour, Eggs, Milk, Baking powder, Sugar
fields.instructions: 1. Mix batter. 2. Fry in a pan. 3. Serve with syrup.

fields.title: Mushroom Risotto
fields.description: A creamy risotto made with Arborio rice, mushrooms, and Parmesan cheese.
fields.ingredients: Arborio rice, Mushrooms, Onion, Vegetable broth, Parmesan cheese
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté onions and mushrooms. 2. Add rice and broth gradually. 3. Stir in Parmesan.

fields.title: Caprese Salad
fields.description: A fresh salad made with tomatoes, mozzarella, basil, and balsamic glaze.
fields.ingredients: Tomatoes, Mozzarella, Fresh basil, Balsamic glaze, Olive oil
fields.instructions: 1. Slice tomatoes and mozzarella. 2. Layer with basil. 3. Drizzle with olive oil and balsamic.

fields.title: Baked Ziti
fields.description: A hearty pasta dish baked with marinara sauce and cheese.
fields.ingredients: Ziti pasta, Marinara sauce, Mozzarella cheese, Ricotta cheese, Parmesan cheese
fields.instructions: 1. Cook pasta. 2. Mix with marinara and cheeses. 3. Bake until golden.

fields.title: Mac and Cheese
fields.description: A super cheesy dish with three different cheeses!
fields.ingredients: Macaroni pasta, Milk, Mozzarella cheese, Ricotta cheese, Cheddar cheese
fields.instructions: 1. Cook pasta. 2. Mix in milk and cheeses.
